      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start, really captures the atmosphere. To make the tension even more immediate, I need to introduce some life into the scene. Can you add some descriptions of some of the people walking through these streets or hanging out on the corners? I want the reader to see the specific types of people who live there so they know exactly what kind of environment they're dealing with. It should feel very authentic to a high-crime area.",
